        "address": {
          "@type": "PostalAddress",
          "streetAddress": "75 E 12300 S Suite 100",
          "addressLocality": "Draper",
          "addressRegion": "UT",
          "postalCode": "84020"
        },
        "areaServed": ["Draper", "Sandy", "South Jordan", "Riverton", "Lehi", "Highland", "Alpine", "Salt Lake County", "Utah County"]
      }
    }
    </script>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-white text-slate-900 font-sans antialiased selection:bg-blue-500 selection:text-white">
    <!-- Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->
    <noscript><iframe src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=GTM-52DJTWGN"
    height="0" width="0" style="display:none;visibility:hidden"></iframe></noscript>
    <!-- End Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->
    <Header />

    <!-- Hero -->
    <Section background="white" class="pt-32 pb-20 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[800px] h-[500px] bg-blue-100/40 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>
      <Container class="relative z-10">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <a href="/#services" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-blue-600 font-semibold mb-6 hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" /></svg>
            All Services
          </a>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-6 leading-[1.05]">
            Knee & Hip Injury Treatment in Utah – <span class="text-blue-600">Immediate Orthopedic Access</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-500 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-4">
            Knee and hip pain can significantly limit mobility and daily function. Whether caused by sports activity, a workplace injury, or gradual degeneration, prompt orthopedic evaluation improves long-term outcomes.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-500 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-8">
            At Instant Orthopedic Care, we provide same-day knee and hip injury treatment in Utah without referral delays. Instead of waiting weeks to see a specialist, patients can walk in and receive comprehensive joint evaluation immediately.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
            <a href="https://pp-wfe-101.advancedmd.com/163338/onlineintake/demographic" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold rounded-full shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/25 hover:bg-blue-700 transition-all hover:scale-105 active:scale-95">Check In Now</a>
            <a href="tel:3853867026" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 border border-slate-200 text-slate-700 font-bold rounded-full hover:border-blue-200 hover:text-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-50/50 transition-all">(385) 386-7026</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Container>
    </Section>

    <!-- ACL & Ligament -->
    <Section background="gray" class="py-24">
      <Container>
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-6">ACL, Meniscus & Ligament Injuries</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Ligament tears often present with swelling, instability, or a popping sensation at the time of injury. Early diagnosis allows for proper bracing, stabilization, and referral planning when needed. Delayed care can increase joint damage and prolong recovery.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our orthopedic providers perform focused assessments to determine whether conservative management or surgical consultation is appropriate.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          {conditions.map((condition) => (
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 hover:border-blue-200 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">{condition.name}</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">{condition.description}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </Container>
    </Section>

    <!-- Hip Pain -->
    <Section background="white" class="py-24">
      <Container>
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-6">Hip Pain & Arthritis Management</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Hip pain may stem from labral tears, bursitis, muscle strain, or degenerative arthritis. Many patients attribute symptoms to aging, but structured treatment can dramatically improve mobility and comfort.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We offer targeted joint injections, bracing strategies, and structured recovery plans tailored to each patient's activity level and goals.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Dr. Meadows is a board-certified orthopedic surgeon with subspecialty certification in sports medicine, fellowship-trained, with emphasis on arthroscopic shoulder/hip/knee, plus fracture care and joint replacement, practicing in the Sandy/Draper area and affiliated with Lone Peak Hospital.
          </p>
        </div>
      </Container>
    </Section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <Section background="gray" class="py-24">
      <Container>
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-12 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            {faqs.map((faq) => (
              <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100">
                <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">{faq.q}</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">{faq.a}</p>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </Container>
    </Section>

    <!-- Serving Areas -->
    <Section background="white" class="py-24">
      <Container>
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-4">Serving Draper, Salt Lake County & Utah County</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 mb-8">Our Draper clinic provides same-day knee and hip orthopedic care to patients throughout the Wasatch Front.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
            {["Draper", "Sandy", "South Jordan", "Riverton", "Herriman", "Lehi", "Alpine", "Highland", "American Fork", "Pleasant Grove", "Bluffdale", "Midvale"].map((city) => (
              <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 text-slate-700 text-sm font-semibold rounded-full">{city}</span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </Container>
    </Section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <Section background="white" class="pb-24 pt-0">
      <Container>
        <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-[3rem] p-12 md:p-20 text-center relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[400px] bg-blue-600/20 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>
          <div class="relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white tracking-tight mb-6">Don't live with joint pain.<br/><span class="text-blue-400">Walk in today.</span></h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg md:text-xl mb-10 leading-relaxed">Same-day knee and hip evaluation without referral delays.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
              <a href="https://pp-wfe-101.advancedmd.com/163338/onlineintake/demographic" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-blue-500 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-600/30 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1">Check In Now</a>
              <a href="tel:3853867026" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-white/5 text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm">Call (385) 386-7026</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </Container>
    </Section>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
